modName: Dremora - Half Dark Elf and Half Dremora
summary: This is also a mix between two races. One was the Dark Elf and the other Dremora!
descriptionHtml:
Here I tested something if it works when I would add the Dremora Race, and it worked, because it added the Dremora Horns to my character and made the skin really Dark :D

Ps. its the Mix Races System, so it will look like Half Dark Elf and Half Dremora, it also adds the voice of the Dremora!
author: Tanja
